<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>سيد علي للتصميم</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@300;400;600;700;900&family=Almarai:wght@300;400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ════════════════════════════════
   كل الإعدادات في مكان واحد ⬇️
   ════════════════════════════════ */
:root {
  --black:#060810; --dark:#0a0d14; --dark2:#0f1320; --dark3:#141827;
  --gold:#C9993A; --gold2:#E8C06A; --gold3:#F5D98A;
  --cyan:#00E5FF; --cyan2:#00B8D9;
  --white:#F0F4FF; --white2:rgba(240,244,255,0.65); --white3:rgba(240,244,255,0.12);
  --ease:cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--white);font-family:'Cairo',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;cursor:none;}

/* ── CURSOR ── */
#cur{width:10px;height:10px;background:var(--cyan);border-radius:50%;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--cyan);}
#cur-r{width:36px;height:36px;border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.4);border-radius:50%;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:transform .5s var(--ease),width .4s,height .4s;}
#cur-r.h{width:56px;height:56px;}

/* ── CIRCUIT BG ── */
.cbg{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;opacity:0.15;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(0,229,255,0.15) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,229,255,0.15) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse 120% 80% at 50% 0%,black 0%,transparent 70%);}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;width:100%;z-index:1000;padding:0 48px;height:70px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;transition:background .5s;}
nav.stuck{background:rgba(6,8,16,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.1);}
.nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;text-decoration:none; cursor: pointer;}
.logo-shield{width:44px;height:50px;flex-shrink:0;}
.logo-text-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1.1;}
.logo-ar{font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold2);letter-spacing:.5px;}
.logo-en{font-size:10px;color:var(--cyan);letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;}
.nav-phone{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold2));color:var(--black);padding:8px 18px;border-radius:4px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;transition:transform .3s,box-shadow .3s;white-space:nowrap;}
.nav-phone:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(201,153,58,0.4);}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none;}
.nav-links a{color:var(--white2);font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;position:relative;transition:color .3s;}
.nav-links a::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-4px;right:0;width:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--cyan),var(--gold));transition:width .4s var(--ease);}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--cyan);}
.nav-links a:hover::after{width:100%;}

/* ── HERO ── */
#hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:90px 48px 60px;}
.hero-glow{position:absolute;top:-200px;right:-150px;width:700px;height:700px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,229,255,0.07) 0%,transparent 65%);pointer-events:none;}
.hero-mosque{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:260px;pointer-events:none;opacity:0.09;}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:680px;}
.hero-eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3);background:rgba(0,229,255,0.05);padding:7px 18px;border-radius:100px;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:2.5px;color:var(--cyan);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:32px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);animation:up .7s var(--ease) .2s forwards;}
.eye-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--cyan);animation:blink 2s ease infinite;}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}
.hero-h1{font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5.5vw,72px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:24px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);animation:up .9s var(--ease) .4s forwards;}
.hero-h1 .g{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold3));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;}
.hero-h1 .c{color:var(--cyan);}
.hero-p{font-size:17px;color:var(--white2);line-height:1.9;max-width:540px;margin-bottom:44px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);animation:up .9s var(--ease) .6s forwards;}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);animation:up .9s var(--ease) .8s forwards;}
.btn-gold{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),#a87420);color:var(--black);padding:15px 32px;border-radius:6px;font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;text-decoration:none;cursor:none;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:transform .3s,box-shadow .3s;}
.btn-gold:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 16px 50px rgba(201,153,58,.45);}
.btn-cyan{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:transparent;color:var(--cyan);padding:14px 32px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.35);font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;cursor:none;transition:all .3s;}
.btn-cyan:hover{background:rgba(0,229,255,0.07);transform:translateY(-3px);}
.hero-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;margin-top:60px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);animation:up 1s var(--ease) 1s forwards;}
.chip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:var(--dark2);border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.12);padding:16px 22px;border-radius:10px;transition:all .3s;flex:1;min-width:140px;}
.chip:hover{border-color:rgba(0,229,255,.4);transform:translateY(-4px);}
.chip-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(0,229,255,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0;}
.chip-text{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.4;}
.chip-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--cyan);font-weight:600;margin-top:2px;}
@keyframes up{to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

/* ── SECTIONS ── */
section{padding:110px 48px;position:relative;}
.sec-label{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--cyan);text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px;}
.sec-label::before{content:'';width:28px;height:2px;background:var(--cyan);border-radius:2px;}
.sec-h2{font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3.8vw,50px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:16px;}
.sec-h2 .g{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold3));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;}
.sec-h2 .c{color:var(--cyan);}
.sec-p{font-size:16px;color:var(--white2);line-height:1.9;max-width:540px;}

/* ── SERVICES ── */
#services{background:var(--dark);}
.services-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin-top:56px;}
.srv-card{background:var(--dark2);border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.08);border-radius:14px;padding:38px 30px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:all .4s var(--ease);cursor:none;}
.srv-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;right:0;left:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--cyan),transparent);transform:scaleX(0);transition:transform .5s;}
.srv-card:hover::before{transform:scaleX(1);}
.srv-card:hover{border-color:rgba(0,229,255,0.25);transform:translateY(-8px);box-shadow:0 24px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.4);}
.srv-card.gold-card:hover{border-color:rgba(201,153,58,0.35);}
.srv-num{font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:56px;font-weight:800;color:rgba(0,229,255,0.05);position:absolute;top:12px;left:18px;line-height:1;}
.srv-icon{width:58px;height:58px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(0,229,255,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:26px;margin-bottom:22px;}
.srv-title{font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px;}
.srv-desc{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--white2);line-height:1.85;}
.srv-tag{display:inline-block;margin-top:20px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--cyan);border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.2);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:100px;text-transform:uppercase;}
.srv-badge{position:absolute;top:20px;left:20px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold2));color:var(--black);font-size:10px;font-weight:800;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:100px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;}

/* ── WHY ── */
#why{background:var(--dark);}
.why-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin-top:56px;}
.why-card{background:var(--dark2);border-radius:14px;border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.07);padding:36px 28px;transition:all .4s var(--ease);cursor:none;}
.why-card:hover{border-color:rgba(201,153,58,0.3);transform:translateY(-6px);box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.35);}
.why-icon{width:54px;height:54px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(201,153,58,.09);border:1px solid rgba(201,153,58,.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;margin-bottom:20px;}
.why-title{font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;}
.why-desc{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--white2);line-height:1.85;}

/* ── CONTACT ── */
#contact{background:var(--black);text-align:center;}
.contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;max-width:700px;margin:48px auto 0;}
.c-card{background:var(--dark2);border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.09);border-radius:12px;padding:28px 20px;transition:all .3s;}
.c-card:hover{border-color:rgba(0,229,255,.25);transform:translateY(-4px);}
.c-card-icon{font-size:28px;margin-bottom:12px;display:block;}
.c-card-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--cyan);letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;}
.c-card-val{font-size:14px;color:var(--white);font-weight:700;}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{background:var(--dark);border-top:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.07);padding:32px 48px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;}
.foot-copy{font-size:13px;color:var(--white2);}

/* ── REVEAL ── */
.r{opacity:0;transform:translateY(36px);transition:opacity .8s var(--ease),transform .8s var(--ease);}
.r.v{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.r.d1{transition-delay:.1s}.r.d2{transition-delay:.2s}.r.d3{transition-delay:.3s}
.neon-div{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--cyan),var(--gold),transparent);opacity:.2;}

/* ════════════════════════════════
   🎛️ لوحة التحكم (ADMIN PANEL) - مخفية بذكاء
   ════════════════════════════════ */
#admin-toggle{
  position:fixed;bottom:30px;left:30px;z-index:99999;
  width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold2));
  color:var(--black);border:none;font-size:24px;cursor:pointer;
  box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(201,153,58,.5);
  transition:transform .3s,box-shadow .3s;
  display:none; /* إخفاء افتراضي */
  align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
#admin-toggle:hover{transform:scale(1.1) rotate(15deg);}

#admin-panel{
  position:fixed;bottom:100px;left:30px;z-index:99998;
  width:360px;max-height:75vh;overflow-y:auto;
  background:#0d1117;border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.25);
  border-radius:16px;padding:24px;
  box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.7),0 0 40px rgba(0,229,255,.1);
  display:none;
  scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:rgba(0,229,255,.3) transparent;
}
#admin-panel.open{display:block;animation:panelIn .4s var(--ease);}
@keyframes panelIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

.ap-header{
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
  margin-bottom:20px;padding-bottom:16px;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
}
.ap-title{font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold2);}
.ap-subtitle{font-size:11px;color:var(--cyan);letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:2px;}
.ap-close{background:none;border:none;color:var(--white2);font-size:20px;cursor:pointer;transition:color .3s;}
.ap-close:hover{color:var(--cyan);}

.ap-section{margin-bottom:20px;}
.ap-section-title{
  font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--cyan);
  text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.ap-section-title::before{content:'';width:16px;height:1px;background:var(--cyan);}

.ap-field{margin-bottom:12px;}
.ap-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--white2);margin-bottom:5px;display:block;font-weight:600;}
.ap-input{
  width:100%;background:#0a0f1a;
  border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
  border-radius:6px;padding:9px 12px;
  color:var(--white);font-family:'Cairo',sans-serif;font-size:13px;
  transition:border-color .3s;outline:none;
}
.ap-input:focus{border-color:var(--cyan);box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,229,255,.1);}
.ap-input[type="color"]{height:38px;padding:4px 8px;cursor:pointer;}
textarea.ap-input{resize:vertical;min-height:70px;}

.ap-save{
  width:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold2));
  color:var(--black);border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;
  font-family:'Almarai',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;
  cursor:pointer;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;margin-top:8px;
}
.ap-save:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(201,153,58,.4);}
.ap-save:active{transform:translateY(0);}

.ap-success{
  display:none;text-align:center;padding:10px;
  background:rgba(0,229,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,.3);
  border-radius:6px;color:var(--cyan);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;
  margin-top:8px;
}
.ap-success.show{display:block;animation:fadeIn .4s;}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}

.ap-divider{height:1px;background:rgba(0,229,255,.08);margin:16px 0;}

/* responsive */
@media(max-width:768px){
  nav{padding:0 20px;}section{padding:80px 20px;}#hero{padding:100px 20px 60px;}
  .services-grid,.why-grid,.contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .hero-chips{flex-direction:column;}
  footer{flex-direction:column;text-align:center;padding:24px 20px;}
  .nav-links{display:none;}
  #admin-panel{width:calc(100vw - 40px);left:20px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="cur"></div>
<div id="cur-r"></div>
<div class="cbg"></div>
<canvas id="cvs" style="position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></canvas>

<nav id="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo" id="secret-trigger">
    <svg class="logo-shield" viewBox="0 0 44 50" fill="none">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="sg" x1="0" y1="0" x2="44" y2="50" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#E8C06A"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#C9993A"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <path d="M22 2L4 9V24C4 34.5 11.5 44 22 48C32.5 44 40 34.5 40 24V9L22 2Z" fill="rgba(0,229,255,0.05)" stroke="url(#sg)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <path d="M22 8L10 13V24C10 31 15 37.5 22 40C29 37.5 34 31 34 24V13L22 8Z" fill="none" stroke="url(#sg)" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.5"/>
      <text x="22" y="29" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Almarai,Cairo,sans-serif" font-size="14" font-weight="800" fill="url(#sg)">م</text>
    </svg>
    <div class="logo-text-wrap">
      <span class="logo-ar" id="e-logo-ar">سيد علي للتصميم</span>
      <span class="logo-en" id="e-logo-en">Sayed Ali Design</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">الخدمات</a></li>
    <li><a href="#why">من نحن</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">تواصل</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#" class="nav-phone" id="e-nav-phone-link">
    📞 <span id="e-phone">07772334785</span>
  </a>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <svg class="hero-mosque" viewBox="0 0 1440 260" fill="none" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMax meet">
    <path d="M0 260V180L60 150V120L80 100L100 120V150L140 180V200L180 150V100L210 60L240 100V150L280 200V180L320 140V80L360 40L400 80V140L440 180V160L490 100V50L530 10L570 50V100L610 160V140L660 80V30L700 0L740 30V80L780 140V160L820 100V50L860 10L900 50V100L940 160V140L990 80V30L1030 0L1070 30V80L1110 140V180L1150 150V100L1180 80L1200 100V150L1240 180V200L1280 150V120L1320 100L1340 120V150L1380 180L1440 160V260H0Z" fill="url(#mg)"/>
    <defs><linearGradient id="mg" x1="720" y1="0" x2="720" y2="260" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#00E5FF"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#00E5FF" stop-opacity="0.1"/></linearGradient></defs>
  </svg>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow"><div class="eye-dot"></div><span id="e-eyebrow">بغداد · العراق · خدمات رقمية متكاملة</span></div>
    <h1 class="hero-h1">
      <span id="e-h1-1">سيد علي</span><br>
      <span class="g" id="e-h1-2">المهندس الرقمي</span><br>
      <span id="e-h1-3">لمشروعك </span><span class="c" id="e-h1-4">القادم.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-p" id="e-hero-p">من تصميم اللوغو إلى بناء التطبيقات.. نحن لا نصمم فقط، <strong>نحن نبني أنظمة تجلب الأرباح.</strong></p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#" class="btn-gold" id="e-btn1-link"><span id="e-btn1">💬 استشارة مجانية الآن</span></a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn-cyan" id="e-btn2">🎯 استكشف الخدمات</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-chips">
      <div class="chip"><div class="chip-icon">📱</div><div><div class="chip-text" id="e-chip1-t">منيو QR الذكي</div><div class="chip-sub" id="e-chip1-s">جاهز بـ 24 ساعة</div></div></div>
      <div class="chip"><div class="chip-icon">🎨</div><div><div class="chip-text" id="e-chip2-t">تصميم لوغو وهوية</div><div class="chip-sub" id="e-chip2-s">براندنج احترافي</div></div></div>
      <div class="chip"><div class="chip-icon">📲</div><div><div class="chip-text" id="e-chip3-t">تصميم تطبيقات</div><div class="chip-sub" id="e-chip3-s">UI/UX حديث</div></div></div>
      <div class="chip"><div class="chip-icon">📣</div><div><div class="chip-text" id="e-chip4-t">تسويق رقمي</div><div class="chip-sub" id="e-chip4-s">مستهدف وذكي</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="neon-div"></div>

<section id="services">
  <div class="r"><div class="sec-label">خدماتنا</div></div>
  <h2 class="sec-h2 r d1">باقات مصممة<br><span class="g">لنجاح مشروعك</span></h2>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="srv-card r d1">
      <div class="srv-num">01</div>
      <div class="srv-icon">🛡️</div>
      <div class="srv-title" id="e-s1-t">براندنج وهوية تجارية</div>
